Description: remove failing tests that prevent installation
 The testing script references a non-existing video.mp4 that causes the script
 to fail, which prevents cmake to install the files to their target location.
Author: Roland Hieber <rohieb@rohieb.name>

--- nordlicht-0.3.0.orig/CMakeLists.txt
+++ nordlicht-0.3.0/CMakeLists.txt
